ZH: 我梦想着成为一名航海家。
EN: I dream of becoming a sailor.

ZH: 他在大海上航海了十年。
EN: He has been sailing at sea for ten years.

ZH: 我们要开始进行航海训练。
EN: We are going to start maritime training.

ZH: 航海者必须学会如何使用导航设备。
EN: Sailors must learn how to use navigation equipment.

ZH: 航海是一项冒险的职业。
EN: Sailing is an adventurous profession.

ZH: 我的爷爷曾经是一名航海冒险家。
EN: My grandfather was once a maritime adventurer.

ZH: 航海让我感到自由。
EN: Sailing makes me feel free.

ZH: 航海要求对风向和潮汐有深刻了解。
EN: Sailing requires a deep understanding of wind and tides.

ZH: 航海的历史可以追溯到几千年前。
EN: The history of sailing can be traced back thousands of years.

ZH: 航海是我们祖先的重要技能。
EN: Sailing was an important skill of our ancestors.

ZH: 航海员面对着许多危险。
EN: Sailors face many dangers.

ZH: 航海充满了挑战。
EN: Sailing is full of challenges.

