EN: Sailing requires courage and patience.

ZH: 航海使我不断学习。
EN: Sailing makes me constantly learn.

ZH: 航海让我感到亲近大自然。
EN: Sailing makes me feel close to nature.

ZH: 航海成为我的爱好和工作。
EN: Sailing has become my hobby and job.

ZH: 航海让我探索世界。
EN: Sailing lets me explore the world.

ZH: 航海需要对海洋环境有深入了解。
EN: Sailing requires a deep understanding of the marine environment.

ZH: 航海是我一生最大的热情。
EN: Sailing is my greatest passion in life.
